metadata.name: The One With My Love
metadata.description:
Dream 001

Love is everything.  
Love is pure joy.  
Love is endless.  
Love is unconditional.  
Love is life.  
Love is selfless.  
Love is transformative.  
Love is worth it.  
Love is healing.  
Love is beautiful.
